<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.5.4">
<l>tāyvāyil coṟkēḷāḷ taṉṉāyat tōṭaṇaiyāḷ taṭameṉ koṅkai</l>
<l>yēyārac cāntaṇiyā ḷemperumāṉ tiruvaraṅka meṅkē yeṉṉum</l>
<l>pēymāya mulaiyuṇṭiv vulakuṇṭa peruvayiṟṟaṉ pēcil naṅkāy</l>
<l>māmāya ṉeṉmakaḷaic ceytaṉakaḷ maṅkaimīr matikki lēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>She does not hear the words from her mother’s mouth;</l>
<l rend="indent">she does not join with her friends.</l>
<l>She does not adorn [herself] with sandal paste to cover her soft, wide breasts;</l>
<l rend="indent">she asks, “Where is our lord’s sacred Araṅkam?”</l>
<l>Ladies, don’t speak of the one with a huge belly who ate this world,</l>
<l rend="indent">having eaten from the demon’s breast so she died.</l>
<l>Women, I cannot figure out  what the great deceiver did to my daughter!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
